\par \fs16 \pard \ql \li600\ri0 \sb0 \fi0 n17 Hartenstein, \b0 \i \ul0 supra\b0 \i0 \ul0  note 5. Similarly, Alhambra elementary schools predicted that the statute would drive out 200 to 300 students over the summer. \b0 \i \ul0 Ibid.\b0 \i0 \ul0 
