\par \fs16 \pard \ql \li600\ri0 \sb0 \fi0 n47 Decl. of Tony Estrada, \b0 \i \ul0 United States v. Arizona,\b0 \i0 \ul0  2:10-cv-01413-SRB, (D. Ariz., filed Jul. 6. 2010), at 5.
