\par \pard \ql \li0\ri0 \sb120 \fi360 Shortly after its passage, two men wearing camouflage outfits shot at and wounded several Latino immigrants near a border town in southern Arizona. n66 The murder of a third-generation, native-born American Latino man in Phoenix was also linked to S.B. 1070's passage. n67 Allowing the Enjoined  \b \i0 \ul0 [*32]\b0 \i0 \ul0   Provisions to take effect would exacerbate these problems by encouraging and reinforcing the cultural suspicion that all Latinos are undocumented immigrants and criminals. n68
