\par \fs16 \pard \ql \li600\ri0 \sb0 \fi0 n68 In February 2011, a militant border vigilante was sentenced to death for the May 30, 2009 Pima County murders of a Latino man and his nine-year-old daughter. The vigilante believed the man was a drug dealer and planned to steal from him in order to fund her radical border patrol organization. Dean Schabner, \b0 \i \ul0 Border Vigilante Shawna Forde Sentenced to Death for Home Invasion,\b0 \i0 \ul0  ABC NEWS, Feb. 22, 2011, http://abcnews.go.com/US/minutemen-vigilante-shawna-forde-sentenced-death-deadly-arizona/story?id=12976687.
