\par \pard \ql \li0\ri0 \sb120 \fi360 The resulting harm to Latinos and to the general public cannot be exaggerated. If a substantial portion of the population fears and distrusts the police, the essential relationship between the police and those they are meant to protect is distorted and a valuable  \b \i0 \ul0 [*34]\b0 \i0 \ul0   investigative tool is diminished. n72
