\par \pard \ql \li0\ri0 \sb120 \fi360 These economic consequences are not limited to businesses that are owned by or cater to Latinos. Immigrants provide a huge financial benefit to Arizona's economy. n81 One recent report estimated that the purchasing power of Arizona's Latinos totaled $ 33.9 billion in 2010. n82 The Arizona legislation targeting Latinos already has produced  \b \i0 \ul0 [*39]\b0 \i0 \ul0   an adverse economic impact throughout the state. n83 As a result, in addition to the other harmful effects, overturning the preliminary injunction would severely disrupt Arizona's economy at a time when Arizona's residents can ill afford it. n84
